com.netflix.genie.client.interceptors

Class JobExecutionModeInterceptor

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.netflix.genie.client.interceptors.JobExecutionModeInterceptor
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    okhttp3.Interceptor

    public class JobExecutionModeInterceptor
extends java.lang.Object
implements okhttp3.Interceptor
    A temporary interceptor to be used during migration from V3 embedded execution to V4 agent execution. Allows clients to force one way or another if desired or if neither just rely on the default behavior of the server.
    Since:
    4.0.0
